WELCOME-POPUP.TITLE: Welcome to the Market Data Engine
WELCOME-POPUP.CONTENT_0:
The application offers you an easy access to one of the most powerful data bases in the automotive aftermarket.

Ready to explore your unique opportunities?

Take a few moments and discover how the Market Data Engine can help you to boost your business with new insights and analyses.
WELCOME-POPUP.CONTENT_1: With your booked licence package you have access to the following countries and functionalities:
WELCOME-POPUP.CONTENT_2:
The main menu on the left hand side allows you to navigate through all licensed modules.

On the next pages, we will guide you through the main points of this menu.

Click on the button to continue.
WELCOME-POPUP.CONTENT_3: Start here and enter an OE or IAM or Wholesaler part number to receive all basic information about the part.
WELCOME-POPUP.CONTENT_4: Go one step further, get more context and discover further potentials in your portfolio and pricing with specialized modules.
WELCOME-POPUP.CONTENT_5: Scale it up - process large lists of IAM and OE part numbers to get all part information at once.
WELCOME-POPUP.CONTENT_6: Assess the competitive situation of your complete parts portfolio through the unique combination of offer intensity and price distance towards the IAM
WELCOME-POPUP.CONTENT_8: Go into detail - analyze your IAM competitors price positioning on different price levels for a tailor-made part basket based on manually created cross-references by Eucon
WELCOME-POPUP.CONTENT_9: This section allows to organize your own favorites, sets, parts baskets, downloads and export definitions to use PartsPool® more efficiently and customized for your own specific use cases.
WELCOME-POPUP.CONTENT_10: This section allows you to manage your team´s user accounts and licenses.
WELCOME-POPUP.LABEL_11: How to get help in the Market Data Engine?
WELCOME-POPUP.CONTENT_11:
• i Icon
    You will find an i-Icon on every page with frequently asked questions and answers to this specific module.
  • FAQ section
    Want to learn more? Check out our full FAQ´s in our Help&Support section and get some helpful tips on how to get the most out of the Market Data Engine.
  • Support
    If you have a more specific question, please contact our support team via phone or email.

Now that you are familiar with the general functionalities of the MDE it´s time to run your first analysis!
